{"tid":1693922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(清算黨鐵）係唔係可以去申訴專員投訴？","createTime":"2019-11-05T01:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T01:34:15.000Z","uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef686791fda14dcc017b5897a08dfbcc8735fcf","tid":1693922,"uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:13:58.000Z","msg":"話說之前黨鐵裝左支那電閘個時我就盡好市民責任去1823舉報佢疑似違反消防條例，之後屋宇署回覆已就港鐵增設活動鐵閘事宜作出審視 ，相關事項應由機電工程署處理，就轉介機電署。<br />\n<br />\n到今日收到機電署回覆，話港鐵公司已向相關政府部門呈交上述保安閘資料作審核，有關裝置沒有對緊急逃生通道和無障礙通道構成影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GYinykn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGYinykn.png&h=241a346b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係我係中科fb 見到機電署話黨鐵避免漏電就已經唔插電。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tZ2ykw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tZ2ykw.png&h=34a10869&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiG8tTT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiG8tTT.png&h=62358559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問題黎啦，如果政府已經審核過無問題，咁黨鐵做乜唔按照正常插電使用呢？同埋點解機電署回覆我同中科個版本係唔同？<br />\n<br />\n請巴打們賜教，一齊盡好市民責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3007c49302d548813e9acea18f9f7656ae5472","tid":1693922,"uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"係唔係機電署講大話？"}]}